abstract: Centers for Disease Control and Prevention releases report showing spike in sexually transmitted diseases syphilis, gonorrhea and chlamydia from 2013 to 2014.
lead_paragraph: Syphilis, gonorrhea and chlamydia are rising at alarming rates, according to figures released by the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention.
